# <%= current_page.data.title %>

The DSKI Summer Camp is a specially designed camp for curious makers to construct, tinker and engineer, with a strong focus on developing ​soft skills​ and ​independence​.

In an intentionally set-up space, makers will learn to manage their time, resources and ideas while having fun, working out ways to ​solve problems as they create exciting projects through ​experimentation​ and ​discovery​.

A linguistic component has been added to our camp this year to provide a fun platform for creative expression.

