## Description

**WEEK ONE - Dingle Dangle Puppets**

Explore the world of puppetry, develop linguistic skills, write original scripts and stage a puppet show.<br>
Field Trip : Muji+ Creative Studio

**WEEK TWO - Movers and Shakers**

Design circuits, code games, build and code a robot, design a robot maze and create other movable projects.<br>
Field Trip : Kawasaki Good Times World

**WEEK THREE - Work with Wood**

Use tools safely to construct with wood, use design thinking to create practical pieces, integrate technology and circuitry into finished projects.<br>
Field Trip : Takenaka Carpentry Tools Museum

**WEEK FOUR - Out of the Box**

Indulge in creative cardboard construction, build movable automation, understand how gears work and create a mechanical toy.<br>
Field Trip : Arimata Toys and Automata Museum

## Field Trips

Field trips are included to provide campers a chance to extend their learning outside the classroom.

* Muji+ Creative Studio
* Kawasaki Good Times World
* Arima Toys and Automata Museum
* Takenaka Carpentry Tools Museum

